        <!-- Application Letter Section -->
        <section id="application" class="section-content">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">Industrial Attachment Application Letter</h2>
                
                <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
                    <div class="prose max-w-none">
                        <div class="text-right mb-6">
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Legae Chalenyana</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">[Your Address]</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">[City, Postal Code]</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">[Email Address]</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">[Phone Number]</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">[Date]</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="mb-4">
                            <p class="text-gray-600">Hiring Manager</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">[Company Name]</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600">[Company Address]</p>
                        </div>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Subject: Application for Industrial Attachment Position</strong></p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Dear Hiring Manager,</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">I am writing to express my enthusiastic interest in the industrial attachment opportunity at [Company Name], as advertised on [Platform where you saw the advertisement]. As a dedicated [Your Field of Study] student at [Your University/Institution], I am eager to apply my academic knowledge and develop practical skills in a professional environment.</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Throughout my academic journey, I have developed strong competencies in [mention 2-3 key skills relevant to the position]. My coursework in [relevant subjects] has provided me with a solid theoretical foundation, which I am keen to complement with hands-on experience. I have particularly excelled in [mention specific projects or achievements] where I demonstrated [specific abilities].</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">What draws me specifically to [Company Name] is your reputation for [mention something specific about the company - their innovation, values, projects, etc.]. I am impressed by your commitment to [specific company value or project] and believe my skills in [specific skill] and passion for [relevant field] align well with your organizational objectives.</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">During my attachment, I hope to contribute to your team by bringing [mention what you can offer - fresh perspective, specific technical skills, research abilities, etc.]. I am particularly interested in gaining experience in [specific area you want to learn] and developing my abilities in [another specific area].</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">I am available for an industrial attachment from [start date] to [end date] and would welcome the opportunity to discuss how my academic background and enthusiasm can benefit your organization. Thank you for considering my application.</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Sincerely,</p>
                        
                        <p class="text-gray-700">Legae Chalenyana</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mt-6 bg-blue-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-2">Template Instructions</h4>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-blue-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                        <li>Replace bracketed information [ ] with your specific details</li>
                        <li>Customize the skills and experiences to match the company's needs</li>
                        <li>Research the company to make your letter more specific and compelling</li>
                        <li>Keep the tone professional and enthusiastic</li>
                        <li>Proofread carefully before sending</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

