                    <div class="prose max-w-none">
                        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Subject:</strong> Job Application - [Position Title] - Legae Chalenyana</p>
                        
                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Dear [Hiring Manager Name or "Hiring Team"],</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">I am writing to express my interest in the [Position Title] position at [Company Name], which I discovered through [Source - e.g., your company website, job portal, referral].</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">As a [Your Current Status - e.g., dedicated student] with experience in [Your Field], I have developed strong skills in [mention 2-3 key skills relevant to the position]. My background in [mention relevant experience or education] has prepared me to contribute effectively to your team.</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">I have attached my CV and cover letter for your review. I would welcome the opportunity to discuss how my qualifications and enthusiasm can benefit [Company Name].</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Thank you for your time and consideration. I look forward to the possibility of discussing this opportunity further.</p>

                        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">Best regards,</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-700">Legae Chalenyana</p>
                        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">[Your Phone Number] | [Your Email Address]</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="bg-green-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-800 mb-2">Email Best Practices</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-green-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                            <li>Use a professional email address</li>
                            <li>Keep the subject line clear and specific</li>
                            <li>Address the recipient properly</li>
                            <li>Be concise and to the point</li>
                            <li>Proofread for spelling and grammar</li>
                            <li>Attach documents as PDF files</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="bg-purple-50 p-4 rounded-lg">
                        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-800 mb-2">Customization Tips</h4>
                        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-purple-700 text-sm space-y-1">
                            <li>Personalize for each company</li>
                            <li>Mention specific company achievements</li>
                            <li>Highlight relevant skills for the role</li>
                            <li>Research the hiring manager's name</li>
                            <li>Follow up if no response in 1-2 weeks</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
